7545:Drivers/STM32F0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f0xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7546:Drivers/STM32F0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f0xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
